title: 2010.10.10-MotoGP.16.Malaysia.Race.BBC2_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.10.10-MotoGP.16.Malaysia.Race.BBC2_UK-TDMK1.m4v

The Malaysian Grand Prix. Jennie Gow introduces coverage from the Sepang International Circuit, where the 15th meeting of the campaign takes place. Casey Stoner won here for the second time last season, but the Australian trailed Spaniards Dani Pedrosa and Jorge Lorenzo in this year's standings. Commentary by Steve Parrish and Charlie Cox.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, iPad all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
